&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 页脚的版权信息 提供一个模板: &amp;#34;© 2021-2022 AXFBlog 版权所有 [沪ICP102345678号](http://www.beian.miit.gov.cn)&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">copyright&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Footer text, e.g. &amp;#39;© {year} Me&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
